Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.76,0:01:43.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很久没来歌剧院了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.57,0:01:53.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走路真别扭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.10,0:01:56.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我要穿成这种样子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.45,0:01:57.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.97,0:01:59.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我忍着 笨兔子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.87,0:02:00.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.64,0:02:02.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.60,0:02:03.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很适合你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.77,0:02:07.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 是么…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.76,0:02:11.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭候多时了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.42,0:02:13.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹·贝萨流士大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.44,0:02:14.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷姆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.44,0:02:20.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我将带领你们去见我的主人鲁法斯·巴尔马
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.99,0:02:27.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\3c&H666666&\b0\pos(319,372)\blur5}纯白的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.16,0:02:30.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.15,0:02:33.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个巴尔马公爵竟然真的答应会面…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.29,0:02:35.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我也好吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.01,0:02:38.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说是个性情非常古怪的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.48,0:02:40.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还以为会被干脆利落地拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.56,0:02:42.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹 那家伙是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.01,0:02:45.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁法斯·巴尔马公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.46,0:02:47.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是四大公爵之一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.06,0:02:52.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在四大公爵中最长寿的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.28,0:02:53.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.48,0:02:59.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也许会知道那些没有记载的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.40,0:03:01.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹想知道什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.76,0:03:05.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,100年前「沙布利耶之悲剧」的事实
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.29,0:03:08.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那以后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.45,0:03:10.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然好几次呼唤杰克
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.06,0:03:12.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他却都没有出现
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.36,0:03:15.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我想知道真相
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.48,0:03:18.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,导致「沙布利耶之悲剧」的巴司卡瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.68,0:03:23.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阻止悲剧扩大的杰克·贝萨流士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.68,0:03:25.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在场的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.39,0:03:26.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被屠杀的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.71,0:03:30.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都和「沙布利耶之悲剧」有关
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.21,0:03:31.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.27,0:03:34.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴司卡瓦正为了上演第二次悲剧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.09,0:03:37.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞄准四大公爵所有的通往阿嵬茨的门
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.91,0:03:39.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时在寻找格连
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.12,0:03:43.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四大公爵的组织「潘多拉」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.63,0:03:46.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同样要夺取巴司卡瓦所有的最后的门
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.86,0:03:49.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阻止他们的野心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.07,0:03:52.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以双方想要得到的都是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.37,0:03:54.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿嵬茨的意志?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.04,0:03:56.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.24,0:03:59.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,热衷于此也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.70,0:04:02.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过也请你好好关照一下艾丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.31,0:04:06.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在笑脸猫那里见到了她的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.36,0:04:09.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你准备就这样瞒着她吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.33,0:04:13.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.22,0:04:18.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从笑脸猫的世界归来后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.94,0:04:22.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丽丝就不太说起找寻记忆的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.26,0:04:29.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丽丝还是想要找回记忆的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.94,0:04:32.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了 鲁法斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.53,0:04:36.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已把奥兹·贝萨流士 及其一行带来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.33,0:04:42.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么嘛 没有人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.82,0:04:46.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.69,0:04:58.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 这是什么生物?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.19,0:05:02.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 您就是巴尔马公爵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.14,0:05:04.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.18,0:05:06.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.65,0:05:07.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:09.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真无聊 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.92,0:05:13.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大部分人见到我都会惊慌失措
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.20,0:05:16.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你竟然一点反应也没有 太无趣了!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.68,0:05:19.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很抱歉 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.50,0:05:21.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.12,0:05:27.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你拥有无论发生什么都可以可以接受的特技
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.00,0:05:30.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 您真了解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.99,0:05:33.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可什么都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.65,0:05:38.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是戒烟了八次都失败的家伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.43,0:05:40.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么连这…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.68,0:05:43.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有我不知道的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.21,0:05:44.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知识就是力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.07,0:05:47.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知晓就是最大的乐趣!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.22,0:05:49.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.24,0:05:50.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙是笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.07,0:05:52.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难说…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.42,0:06:13.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是场闹剧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.18,0:06:17.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.70,0:06:21.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的知识可不是那种轻易送人的廉价之物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.71,0:06:24.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 想要的话就支付代价吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.36,0:06:26.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,代价吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.22,0:06:28.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.28,0:06:32.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提供我所不知道的知识
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.70,0:06:35.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.00,0:06:41.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 你寻找真相的理由是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.43,0:06:47.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.54,0:06:52.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想知道巴司卡瓦宣告的你的罪孽是什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.55,0:06:55.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道了又能怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.07,0:07:01.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至今为止
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.53,0:07:05.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我害怕伤害别人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.77,0:07:08.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为此而寻找真相
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.66,0:07:10.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.26,0:07:14.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是为了正视自我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.89,0:07:17.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后再重新考虑一切
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.52,0:07:21.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于我而言
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.85,0:07:23.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了特别的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.03,0:07:26.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想寻找自己可以做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.59,0:07:28.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.43,0:07:33.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.85,0:07:38.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据我的知识 你应该你傻笑着说「我不知道」来蒙混过关
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.76,0:07:41.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知不觉间信息更新了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.23,0:07:43.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的知识没有跟上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.28,0:07:48.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不甘心 不甘心 不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.72,0:07:52.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}不甘心 不甘心 不甘心…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.47,0:07:50.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.59,0:07:52.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说了什么不对的话了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.79,0:07:54.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不服!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.89,0:07:56.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.91,0:07:58.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴尔马公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.67,0:08:06.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 不要 不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.35,0:08:09.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 这些人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.48,0:08:10.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.43,0:08:15.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无知给周围造成恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.45,0:08:17.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是也可能相反
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.01,0:08:23.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知晓也会孕育恐惧 我知道 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.09,0:08:26.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有过去的记忆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.87,0:08:29.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这样好吗 这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.92,0:08:33.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的就算想起来也无妨吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.88,0:08:37.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 你为什么会忘记呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.58,0:08:41.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道不是因为你想忘记才忘记的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.81,0:08:45.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想起来的话 也许会更加痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.07,0:08:49.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会痛苦到想死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.36,0:08:53.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前进很可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.96,0:08:55.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停止也很可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.84,0:08:59.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怜啊 好可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.45,0:09:04.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絮絮叨叨的真烦人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.46,0:09:05.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.30,0:09:07.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在笑脸猫那里就已经理解了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.66,0:09:09.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我回去寻求的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.53,0:09:11.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己是为何而生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.23,0:09:14.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是为了让自己向前走下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.75,0:09:16.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是有恐惧随行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.03,0:09:19.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种东西就当作旅伴了!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.86,0:09:21.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你个一看就知道很难吃的肉丸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.05,0:09:25.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你所谓的知识上好好刻下一笔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.07,0:09:27.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要的东西就抢走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.79,0:09:29.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妨碍的家伙就打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.68,0:09:34.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是现在的我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.43,0:09:35.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为染血黑兔的艾丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.84,0:09:42.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.89,0:09:44.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然 艾丽丝很厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.66,0:09:46.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.11,0:09:48.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不也一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.33,0:09:51.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为讨厌原地踏步
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.05,0:09:52.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才前进的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.95,0:09:57.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丽丝和我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.46,0:09:59.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是追寻自我的同志呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.63,0:10:01.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同志?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.58,0:10:05.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是伙伴啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.88,0:10:09.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.88,0:10:12.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉还不错啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.82,0:10:20.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.55,0:10:24.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹的改变
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.95,0:10:28.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有自己被丢下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.67,0:10:40.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知识又没跟上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.07,0:10:41.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.03,0:10:45.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不服!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.94,0:10:45.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}真快乐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.22,0:10:47.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴尔马公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.05,0:10:52.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您一直都拒绝我的会面邀请
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.72,0:10:57.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次却主动邀请我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.63,0:11:03.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目的不是奥兹 而是我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.78,0:11:08.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你所说的「想要信息 就付出代价」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.97,0:11:13.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所掌握的信息中 能引起您的兴趣的恐怕只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.35,0:11:16.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您调查了我的过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.75,0:11:18.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴尔马公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.56,0:11:23.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.11,0:11:25.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红眼的亡灵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.32,0:11:27.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯宾·雷芬纳德
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.25,0:11:29.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布雷克
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.38,0:11:42.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多该现身了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.59,0:11:44.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁法斯·巴尔马
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.75,0:11:54.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.89,0:12:01.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.67,0:12:06.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我用心制作的幻影都弄坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.66,0:12:10.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是让人不爽的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.15,0:12:12.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卖帽子的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.78,0:12:19.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲死了 母亲也死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.34,0:12:21.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.63,0:12:26.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别走 凯宾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.50,0:12:30.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要成孤儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.34,0:12:36.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布雷克
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.83,0:12:38.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可悲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.20,0:12:43.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轻易使用力量 就成这副样子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.02,0:12:52.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不想被随意使用力量制造弱智幻影的人说教
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:53.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴尔马公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.94,0:12:57.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他才是真正的巴尔马公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.67,0:12:59.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.01,0:13:02.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要的东西是你所拥有的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.40,0:13:06.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先让我看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.23,0:13:10.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是凯宾·雷芬纳德的证据
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.75,0:13:11.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.75,0:13:17.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁法斯大人 他现在身体…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.93,0:13:20.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为契约的影响 身体状况恶化
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.81,0:13:22.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的相信是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.71,0:13:24.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你错了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.34,0:13:26.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的情况是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.13,0:13:29.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这已经是第二次了吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.20,0:13:38.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,违法契约者的刻印
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.15,0:13:42.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转过一圈就成这般模样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.23,0:13:44.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丑陋 扭曲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.03,0:13:47.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是与罪人相符的烙印
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.49,0:13:55.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.24,0:14:00.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你不说…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.08,0:14:03.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯宾·雷芬纳德
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.79,0:14:07.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是距今50年前的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.59,0:14:10.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个违法契约者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.47,0:14:12.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每夜在街头徘徊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.04,0:14:16.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将人们作为献给灵体的祭物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.06,0:14:20.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在夜里飘摇的血红的双瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.84,0:14:23.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被称作非人之物 给人们带来恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.60,0:14:25.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此而得名
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.19,0:14:28.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红眼的亡灵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.68,0:14:29.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红眼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.27,0:14:32.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,116人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.54,0:14:35.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽管进献了这么多人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.76,0:14:38.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他似乎还是堕入阿嵬茨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.87,0:14:41.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然堕入了阿嵬茨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.92,0:14:43.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说这话什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.84,0:14:46.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说的是那家伙…你说的是小丑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.04,0:14:50.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此 你想要的是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.18,0:14:53.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将布雷克作为犯罪者抓起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.08,0:14:55.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴尔马公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.24,0:15:04.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说那样也很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.89,0:15:07.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要的是信息
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.73,0:15:10.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从那家伙堕入阿嵬茨开始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.46,0:15:15.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到再次回到这里的时间空白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.77,0:15:17.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要的信息如是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.05,0:15:20.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙去过阿嵬茨的深渊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.02,0:15:22.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是遇到过什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.52,0:15:25.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如阿嵬茨的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.31,0:15:36.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是 哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.40,0:15:40.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刻印的指针转过一周
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.08,0:15:43.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后被锁链拖走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.58,0:15:46.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.40,0:15:49.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.48,0:15:51.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.95,0:16:00.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃醋了 吃醋了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.40,0:16:02.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笑脸猫吃人类的醋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.77,0:16:11.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 稍微安静一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.39,0:16:14.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人被吓坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.43,0:16:24.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的名字是?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.91,0:16:38.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫艾丽丝哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.62,0:16:41.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.69,0:16:48.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿鲁布斯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.68,0:16:49.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直想见您
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.41,0:16:51.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿嵬茨的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.78,0:16:53.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿嵬茨的意志?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.76,0:16:55.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个少女?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.25,0:16:57.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿鲁布斯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.73,0:17:00.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你把他带到这里的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.92,0:17:01.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.07,0:17:08.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.46,0:17:12.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的名字叫凯宾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.65,0:17:14.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在一座很大的府邸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.12,0:17:17.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面作为护卫的骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.78,0:17:21.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是大家都死了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.04,0:17:26.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你不在的时候被杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.28,0:17:29.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没能保护他们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.52,0:17:31.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是最重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.58,0:17:32.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却没有拯救他们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.64,0:17:34.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.05,0:17:40.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你才会来这里的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.87,0:17:43.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了能够拯救那些人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.52,0:17:46.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来到阿嵬茨的人都是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.39,0:17:50.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱着必死之心想要夺回什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.74,0:17:54.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 大家都在中途变得很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.44,0:17:57.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为一直和灵体一起体验着黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.59,0:18:00.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.28,0:18:03.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直到最后都没有迷失自我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.67,0:18:08.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过了许多许多年
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.66,0:18:10.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像笨蛋一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.02,0:18:16.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟敢伤害阿嵬茨的意识 绝不能饶恕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.46,0:18:18.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.03,0:18:25.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想和那个人说说话而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.07,0:18:29.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么妨碍我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.39,0:18:39.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丽丝生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.65,0:18:41.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丽丝生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.45,0:18:42.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不听话的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.09,0:18:45.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被艾丽丝毁掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.31,0:18:47.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.53,0:18:49.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.07,0:18:52.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笑脸猫 我们来跳舞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.84,0:19:03.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是何等的噩梦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.30,0:19:06.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是为了挽回主人的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.54,0:19:10.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是为了时间倒流才来到阿嵬茨的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.09,0:19:13.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很痛苦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.36,0:19:14.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很痛苦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.02,0:19:16.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是阿嵬茨的深渊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.57,0:19:20.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是力量最强的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.72,0:19:23.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它会侵蚀你的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.08,0:19:27.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后很快就会像我们一样变成灵体
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.25,0:19:30.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胡说!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.48,0:19:32.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人怎么会变成灵体…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.02,0:19:34.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.56,0:19:38.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿嵬茨的力量能将人变成灵体
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.93,0:19:41.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也可以赐予无机质以意志
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.63,0:19:45.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且也可以支配一切时间的流动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.43,0:19:49.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格连也这么说过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.91,0:19:50.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格连?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.85,0:19:53.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我讨厌格连
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.83,0:19:56.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他想从我身边夺走那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.96,0:19:58.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基尔巴特和文森特也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.02,0:20:01.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凡是接近他的人都最讨厌了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.90,0:20:03.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.43,0:20:06.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忘了件事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.83,0:20:11.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你变成人偶之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.09,0:20:19.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.82,0:20:20.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要拿它做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.80,0:20:22.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要那只红眼睛做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.59,0:20:25.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会给笑脸猫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.54,0:20:28.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才把他叫来这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.06,0:20:31.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.13,0:20:35.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直认为笑脸猫最适合红眼睛了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.07,0:20:41.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会死…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.62,0:20:43.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会死在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.48,0:20:45.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁都拯救不了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.86,0:20:48.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 凯宾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.31,0:20:53.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要变成孤儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.69,0:20:55.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 我还没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.04,0:21:36.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.03,0:21:38.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.93,0:21:43.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有很多东西流入阿嵬茨了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.33,0:21:48.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是沙布利耶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.34,0:21:51.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好好地按照听到的做了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.90,0:21:55.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人打开了阿嵬茨之门
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.65,0:22:01.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后大家都堕入阿嵬茨了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.98,0:22:07.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 你好 艾丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.99,0:23:43.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)\3c&H000000&}我的心苦苦追求着 那未被填满的莫名之物……
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.52,0:23:46.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)\3c&H000000&}是你杀了杰克!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.69,0:23:50.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)\3c&H000000&}你……不是我所知道的艾丽丝吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.48,0:23:53.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)\3c&H000000&}我将过去『改变了』
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.64,0:23:57.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)\3c&H000000&}那不是我等之流出手就能解决的事情……
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.52,0:24:01.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)\3c&H000000&}你背负沉重罪孽 在堕入的深渊尽头——
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.99,0:24:04.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)\3c&H000000&}你看见了什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.75,0:24:09.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\3c&H000000&}下回 失意的代价